    excerpt: 'A deep dive for engineering leaders into an Enterprise Legacy System Modernization Strategy. Learn how to dismantle monolithic architectures using the Strangler Fig pattern, React, and Next.js. We cover technical debt ROI, phased migration roadmaps, and micro-frontend transitions while avoiding the high-risk \'Big Bang\' rewrite. This guide includes code examples for Next.js middleware proxying and strategies for serverless transitions to ensure your modernization project delivers measurable performance gains and business value.',
