    excerpt: 'Is your enterprise React dashboard crashing after long user sessions? Learn how to fix react memory leaks using advanced heap profiling, useEffect cleanup patterns, and React Query cache management. This technical guide for CTOs and Engineering Managers covers strategies to prevent browser memory bloat, reduce user churn, and optimize infrastructure ROI in high-performance B2B SaaS environments.',
