    excerpt: 'Is your enterprise dashboard lagging? Learn how to achieve a consistent 60FPS in React using WebGL, Web Workers, and advanced data streaming architectures. This guide covers rendering 10k+ data points, reducing re-renders, and fixing memory bloat in high-frequency environments.',
