    title: 'Mastering Framer Motion Performance: Optimizing Animations for Enterprise React Applications to Maintain 60FPS',
    excerpt: 'Discover advanced strategies for optimizing Framer Motion animations in enterprise React applications. Learn how to maintain 60FPS, reduce layout shifts, and integrate high-performance motion into complex dashboards without compromising stability or speed.',
